{"tid":1224780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過左咁多年大家都無變過，沈迷階段性勝利","createTime":"2019-06-15T04:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:31:32.000Z","uid":389,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3f318d98083813864701077cef13daa4c645ccdd","tid":1224780,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"聽到政府暫緩，好多fd都讚好，話贏左，話唔使出街<br />\n<br />\n但其實諗咁深一層，呢招根本係政府既陰招<br />\n<br />\n試下暫緩會唔會令民意平息<br />\n<br />\n如果真係平息到<br />\n<br />\n之後就會溫水煮青蛙<br />\n<br />\n慢慢搵機會推倒重來<br />\n<br />\n所以即使係暫緩，即使係階段性勝利<br />\n<br />\n都有可能比人一鋪清袋<br />\n<br />\n23條、傘運、DQ議員、魚蛋革命、一次又一次中招<br />\n<br />\n點解大家重咁沈迷呢啲糖衣毒藥？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算你真係覺得贏左<br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以做次勝利巡遊？點解要繼續享樂？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更何況呢個政權（唔係政府）<br />\n<br />\n一定會繼續打壓<br />\n<br />\n香港人，可唔可以為自己企硬？笠水衰硬！"},{"pid":"596e6f1dd55f0f60c86b9412d99c444726d66458","tid":1224780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"可以勝利巡遊，接受階段性勝利班人禮拜一會唔會三罷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93efd798d0ecf968ccacf7b62b2844674e666220","tid":1224780,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"596e6f1dd55f0f60c86b9412d99c444726d66458","tid":1224780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"可以勝利巡遊，接受階段性勝利班人禮拜一會唔會三罷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"名句：不了要返工"},{"pid":"f93258be64b8f1c5a899d57deddfb3562375ec0b","tid":1224780,"uid":255373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i